<br>
Slay2 is probably about 8% extra damage vs undead. Dont remember what % of swings but about 1/4 crits are turned into slays. So that would be mabye 0.8% or 0.9% of swings.<br>
<br>
Slay1 is somewhere arround 4% extra damage with about 1/6 crits as slays or about 0.6% of your swings.<br>
<br>
